    "title": "COSCO India is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Mid-Level)",
    "description": "Join the COSCO India family as a Warehouse Manager in Jodhpur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout COSCO India:\nCOSCO India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in WMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with COSCO India!",
